{"tid":1826502,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國產第三代核電技術   華龍一號今年福建開始發電","createTime":"2020-01-16T07:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T08:20:24.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"45d41856d74d39d2171529c54fdec5063d3119ce","tid":1826502,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/0116-1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F0116-1a.jpg&h=551d0ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國是其中一個採用核能發電的國家，現時大陸的核電技術已經發展到第三代，有兩種型號選擇，分別是源於美國引入 Westinghouse Electric 的 AP1000 核電平台改進的國和一號（CAP1400），還有由大陸兩大集團中廣核、核工業各自研發的聯合成果，代號 HRP1000 的華龍一號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早前中核集團宣佈，全球首個使用華龍一號核反應堆的福建福清核電站，福建核電 5 號機組將會在今年開始投入發電。現時福清核電站的 1 至 4 號機組採用第二代改進型壓水堆 M310，而 5、6 號則採用華龍一號，當中 5 號機組是全球第一組，在 2015 年 5 月開工興建，今年正式完工，起著示範作用。今年和其他機組併網發電後，將代表國產第三代核電技術經過多年研發後終於成功。<br />\n<br />\n大陸傳媒報導指，在福清核電站的示範反應堆後，政府在去年 10 月重新啟動大規模核電建設，例如漳州核電 1 號機去年 10 月中開始動工。除了福建和漳州會採用華龍一號，廣西和廣東太平嶺都會採用，而海外則有巴基斯坦採用。根據去年 6 月的數據，中國大陸營運中的核電機組多達 47 台，為全球第三；興建中的核電機組 10 台，規模則是全球第一。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/01/16/made-in-china-3rd-gen-nuclear-tech-fujian/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2Fmade-in-china-3rd-gen-nuclear-tech-fujian%2Flife-tech%2F&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GI429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=b989c259\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/01/16/made-in-china-3rd-gen-nuclear-tech-fujian/life-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"6f93a43f54f68ee8c0b8d450981308a2b423e9f3","tid":1826502,"uid":291465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T07:49:01.000Z","msg":"褔建準備變第二個Pripyat"},{"pid":"1e3ef3cf552eb139bc912f7b030d0219402adab3","tid":1826502,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T07:50:16.000Z","msg":"福建最近台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7f5f3e6d65a7fb6609b8e475bd2e3d4f1f2ca1","tid":1826502,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T07:51:34.000Z","msg":"好大個核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9caa66908dcc523b8935d537fcc5912d63f8de","tid":1826502,"uid":154106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:14:01.000Z","msg":"大陸改進美國，肯定唔係改劣？"},{"pid":"269e788c06c5beca7b113af7e78a8508d89c59d7","tid":1826502,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a9caa66908dcc523b8935d537fcc5912d63f8de","tid":1826502,"uid":154106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:14:01.000Z","msg":"大陸改進美國，肯定唔係改劣？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:17:37.000Z","msg":"馬雲：假貨比真貨好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c8a289daedb2b8f88e6c7228273bf80bb6f136","tid":1826502,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:18:34.000Z","msg":"（新方向）如何令垂死的文宣活動起死回生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1826045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1826045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c6654be7cfe15dcc75d2184d1ff3dfff13c8804a","tid":1826502,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:19:39.000Z","msg":"妳唔肯統一我就引爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9038070dc80a37f0b31834ab65494cb42f3cd21c","tid":1826502,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:20:24.000Z","msg":"冇人傷亡  核爆有益身心"}]}